==English==
===Etymology===
from the Indian cricketer [[w:Vinoo Mankad|Vinoo Mankad]]
===Noun===
'''Mankad'''
#{{cricket}} a [[run out]] of the [[non-striker]] by the [[bowler]] before [[bowling]] the ball if the non-striker leaves his [[crease]] too early; thought by some to be [[ungentlemanly]]

